Phan 1 - Phan tich: Hiem hoa SQL Injection
Khi ban dung code noi chuoi nhu sau:
String sql = "SELECT * FROM patients WHERE name = '" + inputName + "'";

1. Luong thuc thi khi bi tan cong:
Gia su ke xau nhap vao o tim kiem chuoi: ' OR '1'='1
Cau lenh SQL gui den database se tro thanh:
SELECT * FROM patients WHERE name = '' OR '1'='1'

2. Tai sao menh de WHERE luon dung?

Trong SQL, phep toan OR se tra ve True neu mot trong hai ve dung.

Ve thu hai '1'='1' la mot bieu thuc toan hoc luon luon dung.

Ket qua: Database se bo qua dieu kien ve ten va tra ve toan bo du lieu trong
bang patients. Day chinh la cach thong tin benh nhan bi ro ri.